text: Séverine Bonal is an archer from France. She was born on 13 February 1972. Bonal competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics.Séverine BonalSeverine BONAL == References == Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:French archers Category:Olympians for France Category:People from Montpellier Category:Sportspeople from Occitanie
